reviewText:
I was very disapointed with this. The date on the Amazon posting said "2008" so I thought it would be an up-date to the original 1987 VHS video which I have. It isn't. It appears to be simply a transfer of the original 22 year old video to DVD format. New material may have been added because the copyright said 1991. But still ... thats 18 years old!

There are newer and more up to date videos about the Intracoastal Waterway available.
